    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>As part of its 50 years of performing arts anniversary celebrations, Queen Margaret University (QMU) is offering a fully funded Master by Research position.</p>
<p>Prospective students are invited to submit a proposal for how they would investigate and present the history and impact of the various performing arts programmes delivered by QMU over the last 50 years.</p>]]></Value>
